Package: ShennongTools
Type: Package
Title: Unified API for Bioinformatics Tools via YAML Configuration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Songqi", "Duan", , "duan@songqi.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0822-5883"))
  )
Description: Provides a unified API for executing bioinformatics tools
    through YAML configuration files. Supports tool registration, parameter
    validation, template rendering, and command execution with conda/mamba
    environment management.
